$ System.Net.WebUtility (class)
@ System.Net.WebUtility

`HtmlEncode('&')` returns `&amp;`.
-
`HtmlDecode('&amp;')` returns `&`.

`UrlEncode('Foo/bar baz')` returns `foo%2Fbar+baz`.
-
`UrlDecode('foo%2Fbar+baz')` returns `foo/bar baz`.

